Blueprint Core Proposition Key Insight Fitness (C/F/T/Cp) Overall
CONTROL-001-v1.0 ⭐ Shift from Earth open-loop to Martian closed-loop autonomy Framed transition as control theory problem 9/9/8/9 8.75
COGNITIVE-001-v1.0 Transition triggered by Earth control cognitive overload Identified human attention as critical resource 9/8/7/8 8.0
POLITICAL-001-v1.0 Founder's Transition as legitimacy crisis Highlighted governance as central challenge 10/9/6/8 8.25
RELIABILITY-001-v1.0 Triggered by verified fault-tolerance metrics Provided objective engineering criteria 10/7/10/8 8.75
RESOURCE-001-v1.0 Triggered by material flow reversal (Mars > Earth supply) Defined transition in tangible resource terms 10/7/9/9 8.75

Selection Rationale: CONTROL-001 demonstrated superior fertility and compression, providing a framework that could integrate technical autonomy requirements with governance and human factors into a unified model.

A.5 Generation 3: Constitutional Synthesis

Parent: CONTROL-001-v1.0 • Focus: Authority allocation mechanisms, founder psychology modeling, cyber-physical constitution design

