PANOPTICON-001-v1.0 ⭐ Symmetrical transparency + obfuscation rights in Lex Machina Balanced surveillance needs with liberty protections 10/9/8/9 9.0
PROJECTILE-001-v1.0 Meritocratic thrust toward terraforming vector Aligned governance with directional goal 9/8/6/8 7.75

Selection Rationale: PANOPTICON-001 achieved the highest overall fitness, directly addressing the core dilemma of transparency versus liberty with a sophisticated, balanced framework that maintained high testability and fertility.

A.6 Generation 4: Autonomy-Preserving Hybridization

Parent: PANOPTICON-001-v1.0 • Focus: Address drift, psychological burden, founder effects; add Autonomy-Preservation dimension

Blueprint Core Proposition Key Insight Fitness (C/F/T/Cp/AP) Overall
HYBRID-DD-001-v1.0 ⭐ Direct Ledger Democracy: ledger + direct votes on short, sunsetting proposals Hybridized transparency with direct democracy elements 9/9/9/8/9 8.8
